node.text: You guys have been asking me for so long now and I’ve had to keep this secret 🤐 but i can finally say, THE GUYS AND I ARE BACK! Season 3 of @carmastersrusttoriches on @netflix airs August 4th! Make sure you guys tag Netflix and let them know how excited you are, and click the link in my bio to leave comments on the official trailer too 🏁 #carmastersrusttoriches #constancenunes

node.text: Just two more weeks till the new season of #carmastersrusttoriches airs on @netflix ! Make sure you set your alarms for March 27th so you can check out what we have been up to. For now check the trailer here and the link in my bio...Who can guess which car was my favorite build of the season just off this sneak peak? 😍 #carsbyconstance #constancenunes

node.text: So alot of you mentioned that you wouldn’t be bringing your builds out to tomorrows cruise/car show because they weren’t “show cars”...let me just say that #Babystang isn’t perfect...like myself, Babystang has flaws and things to work on all the time, and to be completely honest i wouldnt have it any other way. Babystang is a constant project, it’s my daily driver, thru the years we have been thru all the ups and downs life has to offer together and we have scars to prove it...i could tell you where every ding, every bit of chipped paint, every jimmy-rig part has come from, along with every new upgrade, and where the build is going. It’s not about perfection....if your build is under construction, a $100,000 custom hot rod, or just something you and your buddies built together in your backyard, if they make you happy then they are worth bringing out and showing off. So to cut this off before i continue to ramble, i hope to see you all and all your builds out at tomorrow’s show and at future shows too. Always be proud of what you got 🏁 #constancenunes #carsbyconstance
